  Given a <fr:link
href="algm-000M.xml"
type="local"
addr="algm-000M">ringed</fr:link> topological space, it is <fr:link
href="algm-000L.xml"
type="local"
addr="algm-000L">locally ringed</fr:link> iff every stalk is a local ring.
</fr:p>
  
    
    <fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
toc="false"
numbered="true"
